Rating: 4
I only made a half batch and it was just enough for two first-course servings. Next time, I'll probably make a double batch 'cause it was so good. I added extra garlic and also used fresh thyme in the soup base. I used cooking sherry from the pantry and didn't feel like it was noticeable. Most importantly, just omit the crab; it's an afterthought anyway and doesn't belong--the mushrooms are the star.

