Rating: 3
My husband and I loved this! Instead of using fresh crimini mushrooms, I reconstituted .5 oz of porcini mushrooms in 3/4 c. white wine for 20 minutes and then sauted this (drained mushrooms) with the garlic and onion. I eliminated the step of sauting the mushroom caps. It made the whole process go faster. I will defininetly make this again, and for guests!

