Rating: 4
This recipe is awesome. I agree with the first reviewer though - it doesn't make a whole lot and it's a little pricey. I love crab, BUT I think this recipe would be wonderful without it, too (and a lot less expensive). I used half and half instead of heavy cream which fat-wise doesn't make a huge difference, but it's something, especially since this recipe calls for almost a stick of butter as well. Try this recipe out. It is definitely worth it.

Rating: 4
